OL,3,CStarmer continues farewell tour with
OL,4,CBurnham set for No 10
OL,6,FSir Keir Starmer will continue his
OL,7,Ffinal visit to France as Prime
OL,8,FMinister on Tuesday after Andy Burnham
OL,9,Fwas effectively confirmed as his
OL,10,Fsuccessor.
OL,12,FThe Prime Minister is expected to
OL,13,Fattend Bastille Day celebrations
OL,14,Falongside other world leaders in
OL,15,FParis, where troops from the Grenadier
OL,16,FGuards will march alongside the French
OL,17,FGarde Republicaine.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
