OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1784002678
OL,3,CStarmer continues farewell tour with
OL,4,CBurnham set for No 10
OL,6,FThe celebrations follow Sir Keir's
OL,7,Ffinal "coalition of the willing"
OL,8,Fsummit on Monday, at which fellow
OL,9,Fleaders Emmanuel Macron, Volodymyr
OL,10,FZelensky and Friedrich Merz paid
OL,11,Ftribute to his impact on the world
OL,12,Fstage.
OL,14,FFrench President Mr Macron told Sir
OL,15,FKeir that "we owe you a lot, Prime
OL,16,FMinister", while Mr Merz, the German
OL,17,FChancellor, said he would "phone you
OL,18,Foccasionally to get your opinion on
OL,19,Fthis or that".
