OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1784002678
OL,3,CStarmer continues farewell tour with
OL,4,CBurnham set for No 10
OL,6,FMr Zelensky, the Ukrainian President,
OL,7,Fthanked Sir Keir for his "constant,
OL,8,Fsteadfast support", which the Prime
OL,9,FMinister said would continue under his
OL,10,Fsuccessor.
OL,12,FThat successor is now guaranteed to be
OL,13,FAndy Burnham, the former Greater
OL,14,FManchester mayor, who secured the
OL,15,Fbacking of 349 Labour MPs on Monday.
OL,26,@oD@ZOUpD@RO]
