CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1784002678
OL,3,CStarmer continues farewell tour with
OL,4,CBurnham set for No 10
OL,6,FWith only 54 Labour MPs yet to
OL,7,Fnominate someone for the leadership,
OL,8,Fit is now mathematically impossible
OL,9,Ffor another candidate to secure the 81
OL,10,Fsupporters necessary to mount a late
OL,11,Fchallenge to succeed Sir Keir.
OL,13,FBut Mr Burnham will only be officially
OL,14,Fconfirmed as the new leader on Friday,
OL,15,Fand will formally take over from Sir
OL,16,FKeir three days later on July 20.
OL,18,FDespite being the only candidate, Mr
OL,19,FBurnham took part in an online
OL,20,Fhustings with Labour MPs on Monday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
