PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1784002678
OL,3,CStarmer continues farewell tour with
OL,4,CBurnham set for No 10
OL,6,FParty sources said he used the event
OL,7,Fto set out his priorities for the
OL,8,Fcountry, including devolving power to
OL,9,Fcommunities, improving growth across
OL,10,Fthe UK and tackling the cost of living.
OL,12,FHe also paid tribute to Sir Keir for
OL,13,Fdelivering on his promise of a
OL,14,FHillsborough Law, which is expected to
OL,15,Fclear the Commons on Tuesday after a
OL,16,Fdeal to bring spies within its "duty
OL,17,Fof candour".
OL,26,@xD@`OUyD@KO]
