OL,3,CStarmer continues farewell tour with
OL,4,CBurnham set for No 10
OL,6,FAnd he pledged to lead from the front
OL,7,Fon changing the culture within Labour,
OL,8,Fpromising to be more accountable and
OL,9,Faccessible to MPs and appoint cabinet
OL,10,Fministers from across the party.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/6
